ha\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeevan_Ram_Shrestha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeevan_Ram_Shrestha\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9994308142648364, \"rank\": 0.0005694314742517014, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\", \"score\": 0.995133787650352, \"rank\": 0.004889411579305082, \"text\": \"Bahadur\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international recognition\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"the formation\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few days ago, Minister for Youth and Sports Teju Lal Chaudhary, during a briefing at the ministry, had announced that an ad-hoc NOC committee would be formed with the consent of 22 national sports associations.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teju_Lal_Chaudhary\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teju Lal Chaudhary\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teju_Lal_Chaudhary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teju_Lal_Chaudhary\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9994308142648364, \"rank\": 0.0005694314742517014, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou